!ohne-icon.png|thumbnail!
# It really helps a lot that the title row is fixed in the detail view even when I am scrolling down. Again the issue type icon is missing for me in this title row to easily identify whether I am editing the right ticket or not.

h2. Actual Case
The element with xsl as namespace will be rendered wrongly and the element (class="code-quote">) is added in between.

{code:xml}
<value xsl:type="strict"/>
{code}

h2. Work Around
Use code block render instead of using xml code block but this will lose the xml attribute colour highlight feature.
{code}
<value xsl:type="strict"/>
{code}
